title: Ccls
author: Ccls
content: So about a month and a half ago, my friend told me about https://www.seener.org/en-US/ This things works, but be carefulYou make escrows and they give good daily profits that can be withdraw or escrow again.You can reach it on your wallet web browser (Metamask), simply type dapp.seener.orgThe invitation code is 683535, after that you can invite people yourself. They give benefits by inviting people in.What is important to keep in mind is that Seener launched their Dapp (decentralized application) in august 2022, it hasn’t been long and even if the company is doing well, you never know what might happens if it crashes or any other possible reasons to go down. So this thing works, but do not put high amounts in it unless you like to gamble. Some times when things are too good to be true, you wonder, how long with it last? We don’t know, it works for now, but be careful.Company name: Seener Foundation PTE. LTD.-Authenticated and Licensed by the ACRA (Accounting and Corporate Regulatory Authority) of Singapore. Shown on the ACRA website, but the certificate itself can be given if asked.-UEN (Unique Entity Number): 202122638N-Website: Seener.org-Their social Medias are linked at the bottom right of their home website.- White Paper: Is linked at the bottom left of their home website.
